Author: joey alexander
Title: [ANN][ICO] UBANX - Desinged for everyone, powered by you
Body: Ubanx offered model is fairly ambitious and comprehensive, and has buy-in from some important partners. But whether its partnerships and physical stores will be able to attract enough ordinary users for its ecosystem to take off is impossible to tell in advance. It would not hurt reveal more about its basic services, as well as how exactly the community rewards system will work. But if it can succeed in tapping a new market for cryptocurrencies, it would be able to become a crucial player in the industry during its transition to the mainstream.crypto industry startups are critically dependent on public support. If more people had a working understanding of blockchain technologies and participated in the market.

Author: jUbanx
Title: [ANN][ICO] UBANX - Desinged for everyone, powered by you
Body: We are more than an Idea phase, we past that point long ago. We are a startup company already with real partnerships, which is the core of the functionality of the Ubanx physical Spaces, some of our core partnerships are very well established in Argentina (Transatlantica > fully licensed bank, La Maquinita > top coworking network, Coffee Store > franchising coffee network) and others are global (Trezor, Priority Pass) like others we are in different levels of conversations with (Bancor, Jaxx, tZero, to name a couple). We are going global, Latam is just the very beginning. The first Physical Space will be in argentina and we already have the agreement, as soon as we start we will anounce it in the news, in should be ready before this year ends.
